snippet.title: Mortal Kombat X: Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Check out the launch trailer, directed by System Of A Down’s Shavo Odadjian, with glimpses of iconic moments, a cast of new and returning Kombatants and heart-pounding fight sequences set to the band’s hit song, “Chop Suey!”
